Toxiss <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ustalken.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stalken</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/12/01 4:25:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=544.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RE:</span><hr size=1> What's your kittie's name on Sullon Toxxis? We probably ran in to each other. Not too many cats at all on the server and not to many place on Luclin to go for lowbies right now. So it's a small world on the moon =)<br>
<br>
Not sure how BL's are going to be in pvp... they seem to pve well enough. Unless they're being played by an idiot. As far as BL melee skills at least you can hold those neat looking h2h weapons and look cool and looking cool is half the battle =)<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utoxiss.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Toxiss</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/12/01 4:37:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=544.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> RE:</span><hr size=1> Hi Stalken,<br>
<br>
I am Grahl on SZ, we spoke earlier today.  Hehe, yeah, the cat community is pretty small, but I think more people getting Luclin now.  There were a whopping 15 newb cats in town today at one point!!!  Area around Shar Vahl is pretty empty really.  Some newts and evils in Paludal occasionally, a few Iggles in Hollowshade Moor, and nobody ever in Grimling Forest when I've been there.  Really, the thicket/paludal can easily provide xp up to level 25 and higher for people that don't like to explore much.  So hopefully, some cats level up quick =)<br>
